title: #92Noon Vox In The Box! Mileski/Falness/Russo/Sickman/Ramsey
description: #92Noon returns to the Xcel Energy Center Press Box for the morning skate of the Wild's game against the Arizona Coyotes! There were some technical errors to start the show, so there was some bonus Power Trip! Tenna B is in for the first hour. The Athletic's Michael Russo joins the program, Aaron Sickman is in the Penalty Box, and Rachel Ramsey makes her regular Vox In The Box appearance!
